text: Bout can mean: == People == *Viktor Bout, suspected arms dealer *Jan Everts Bout, early settler to New Netherland == Musical instruments == * The outward- facing round parts of the body shape of violins, guitars, and other stringed instruments == Other == * "Bout" (song), a single by the British artist Jamelia * A boxing match * A roller derby match * An episode of illness
title: Bout
